author: Neil Postman
content: "(Paraphrased) questions to ask of a new technology:\r\n\r\n- What is the\
  \ problem to which this technology is the solution?\r\n- Whose problem is it?\r\n\
  - What new problems might result from solving this problem?\r\n- Which people and\
  \ institutions might be harmed by this solution?\r\n- How does the new technology\
  \ change our language, and what are the implications of that?\r\n- What people and\
  \ institutions gain economic or politcal power because of the technological change?\r\
  \n"
